  "texts": [
    "D. Results: Effectiveness of Counterfactuals as Contrast SetsWe use the same DistilBERT models as in Section V that are fine-tuned for each of the 3 tasks (IMDB, SNLI and AG News).",
    "We evaluate each of these 3 models on both the original test set and the counterfactual one (i.e., the contrast sets) and show these results in Table II.",
    "We obtain the performance values for Polyjuice-generated contrast sets from the original paper [5].",
    "For the 'Expert' baseline, the IMDB contrast sets are created by human experts in [8].",
    "Unfortunately, there does not exist any expert created contrast set for SNLI and AG News datasets."
  ],
